rdrobes, customized furniture, paneling, partitions, and upholstered joinery elements; and precast products, including columns, beams, slabs, staircases, and facade panels. The company was formerly known as Sobha Developers Limited and changed its name to Sobha Limited in August 2014. Sobha Limited was incorporated in 1995 and is headquartered in Bengaluru, India."}}